snippet.title: GEFRAGT GEJAGT Das Spiel Trailer (deutsch/german)
snippet.description:
Enjoy the first trailer from Gefragt - Gejagt, the german quiz game. It will be released October 29th, 2021 on PS4, Switch and PC.
